text.tspan: Maintaining reproducible data workflows while keeping data in sync, backed up, and easily accessible from within and outside
the lab is a key challenge in research. To minimize time and effort scientists have to spend on these tasks, we provide
a suite of tools designed for comprehensive, reproducible and versioned management of scientific data.
